{'dateCreated': <DateTime '20200118T15:55:00' at 0x1a4f29e1588>, 'description': '\n# 限制小数位数\n\n```\n<input type="number" @keydown="handleInput2" placeholder="请输入或查看" v-model="item.SalePrice">\n```\n```\nhandleInput2(e) {\n    // 通过正则过滤小数点后两位\n    e.target.value = (e.target.value.match(/^\\d*(\\.?\\d{0,1})/g)[0]) || null\n},\n```\n\n# 限制整数\n\n```\n<input type="number" @keydown="handleInput" placeholder="请输入" v-model="SaleQty">\n```\n```\nhandleInput(e) {\n// log(e.target.value)\ne.target.value=e.target.value.replace(/[^\\d]/g,\'\');\n},\n```', 'title': 'vue 中 限制 input 输入数字、小数位数等', 'categories': ['[随笔分类]FrontEnd~Vue'], 'enclosure': {'length': 0}, 'link': 'https://www.cnblogs.com/wbyixx/p/12209233.html', 'permalink': 'https://www.cnblogs.com/wbyixx/p/12209233.html', 'postid': '12209233', 'source': {}, 'userid': '-2'}